{"title":"Docker之镜像","date":"2020-02-29T12:14:28.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Feb 29, 2020","L":"02/29/2020","MM-DD":"02-29"},"thumbnail":"post/Docker/Docker之镜像/cover.jpg","link":"post/Docker/Docker之镜像","categories":["Docker"],"updated":"2020-02-29T16:07:50.751Z","content":"<h1 id=\"docker镜像简介\">Docker镜像简介<a href=\"#docker镜像简介\" title=\"Docker镜像简介\"></a></h1><p>Docker中的镜像与容器就像是类和对象的关系。一个镜像由以下要素来标识</p>\n<ul><li>Repository</li>\n<li>Tag</li>\n</ul><h1 id=\"docker镜像常用操作\">Docker镜像常用操作<a href=\"#docker镜像常用操作\" title=\"Docker镜像常用操作\"></a></h1><p><strong>列出镜像</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker images</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<img src=\"/post/Docker/Docker%E4%B9%8B%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F/image-20200229202034312.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<p><strong>拉取镜像</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker pull redis:5.0.7</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<img src=\"/post/Docker/Docker%E4%B9%8B%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F/image-20200229202803204.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<p><strong>查找镜像</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker search redis</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<img src=\"/post/Docker/Docker%E4%B9%8B%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F/image-20200229203003592.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<p><strong>删除镜像</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker rmi redis:5.0.7</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<img src=\"/post/Docker/Docker%E4%B9%8B%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F/image-20200229203243883.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<p><strong>构建镜像</strong></p>\n<ul><li>-t ：指定要创建的目标镜像名</li>\n</ul><figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker build -t myimage:1.0 ./Dockerfile</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><strong>设置镜像标签</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker tag imageId repository:tag</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","prev":{"title":"Docker之网络","link":"post/Docker/Docker之网络"},"next":{"title":"Docker之容器","link":"post/Docker/Docker之容器"},"plink":"https://beginc.github.io/post/Docker/Docker之镜像/","toc":[{"id":"docker镜像简介","title":"Docker镜像简介","index":"1"},{"id":"docker镜像常用操作","title":"Docker镜像常用操作","index":"2"}]}